instructions: Place the fork on the dinner table with the tines pointed up
Place the Dinner knife with the blade pointed up with room for a plate between the fork and knife
Place the Salad Fork right next to the dinner fork to the left with tines up
Place the salad knife right next to the dinner knife on the right with blade up
Put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife with bowl up
Put the desert spoon above the other items perpendicular to them
Now put the desert spoon on the right of the soup spoon with bowl up
Place the desert spoon back to its orginal position
Place the dinner plate between the dinner fork and the dinner knife
Place the bread plate above the forks
Place the butter knife on the bread plate with blade pointed down/left
Place the wine glass above the knifes and spoons
Place the water glass between the dinner plate and the wine glass above
Place the napkin on the dinner plate in the middle
